gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />交通方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公共交通</span></span>工具入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接近集會完分時段走，好難散人<br />\n唔知幾點完 但係11點本身好多人收工<br />\n巴士有d線尾班車 請大家注意時間上車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開車黎既話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />預咗會塞車，1號4號場都好細，塞長龍會塞埋條路，有機會影響巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好係車內外貼支持/反對標語，會比人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">mark車牌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>另外</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />van場係3號停車場，私家車1，4號場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n‼️ AAT 對出既迴旋處開左新既貨車停車場可泊客貨 van ‼️<br />\n有廿幾三十個位<br />\n頭三個鐘每個鐘 20蚊 私家車唔入得<br />\n剩係貨車/客貨車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />200+文宣圖任攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1366027/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1366027/page/1</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(1) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑衫, 口罩</span></span><br />\n(2) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Memo 紙, 文宣紙</span></span>整<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">連儂牆</span></span><br />\nmemo可以痴係範圍內，岀面見memo同事要馬上報比AA知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">leaflet</span></span>有人話唔好派，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">放係到比人拎</span></span>就得<br />\n(3) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Ipad / 電腦 播片</span></span>比外國人睇！！！<br />\n(4) 準備定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">banner，最好係有英文</span></span>!<br />\n<ins>iOS:</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/led-banner-scrolling-text/id1356029756?fbclid=IwAR3QzJIb5OhEyWlpQHeR9EcN58N6IAeCmaJOT7OaHGuNENfY6FS4CU7ZiAo&amp;l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fled-banner-scrolling-text%2Fid1356029756%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3QzJIb5OhEyWlpQHeR9EcN58N6IAeCmaJOT7OaHGuNENfY6FS4CU7ZiAo%26l%3Den&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=0a36172a\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/led-banner-scrolling-text/id1356029756?fbclid=IwAR3QzJIb5OhEyWlpQHeR9EcN58N6IAeCmaJOT7OaHGuNENfY6FS4CU7ZiAo&amp;l=en</a><br />\n<ins>Android:</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=oops.ledscroller&amp;fbclid=IwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Doops.ledscroller%26fbclid%3DIwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=8f5497a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=oops.ledscroller&amp;fbclid=IwAR2XjBA9Ve-uOi9HiYVqsbv1ZVZe8NaYiRNUYNoGtaFF1fAjUPXWY4se1L0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">tablet</span></span>仲正! 會好搶眼!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/do